Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.67,0:01:25.26,OP,,0,0,0,,{\be10\fad(160,160)\pos(1178.667,712.534)}(彩虹一般)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.28,0:01:30.81,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be10\fad(160,160)}七色に光る
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.28,0:01:30.81,OP,,0,0,0,,{\be10\fad(160,160)}閃耀著七色光輝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.83,0:01:33.64,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be10\fad(160,160)}あなだとの時間に
